    <div class="world-content">
      <p>We started in Rimeford, traveled underground to Mineford, and have finally ended in Farholde, the capital city of the realm. It's beautiful, oppressive, ridiculous, and held together by propaganda, fear, and theonite collars.</p>
      <p>Magic is illegal in this realm. Unless you are part of the OT, the anti-magic police force. Magical construct guards patrol the checkpoints. Even the occasional battle of teh carnivals isn't enough to lift peoples' spirits.</p>
      <div class="world-pull">
        <div class="world-pull-text">"Come for the capital city splendor, stay because you were detained at a checkpoint."</div>
        <div class="world-pull-attr">Farholde tourism board (unverified)</div>
      </div>
      <p>Our heroes are tangled in resistance plots, noble weddings, forbidden gods, living batteries, masked identities, family drama, and one very drunk dragon named <em>J'Michael</em>.</p>
